  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"games-frame-pacing-2.1.1\" data-text=\"Version 2.1.1\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.1.1</h3>\n<p>July 10, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.games:games-frame-pacing:2.1.1</code> is released. Version 2.1.1 contains <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/opt/gamesdk/+log/4880f53064c0abc7f2adaa4895e0c9e1c0ade08b..394f81c696e264c403a8491dd6e37aa89e3da00d/games-frame-pacing\">these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Properly unregister display listener from swappy to avoid a hang.</li>\n<li>Fix a crash in <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">ChoreographerFilter::onSettingsChanged</code> using destroyed mutex.</li>\n</ul>",
